    "description": "<!-- MOBILE DESCRIPTION -->\n<div style=\"display:none\">\n<div vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n<span property=\"description\">Meet your forever laces (okay, maybe your almost-forever laces): the ASR Outdoor TraversaLace 550 Paracord Survival Laces for Shoes and Hiking Boots. Constructed from a seven-strand nylon inner core (kern) and exterior nylon jacket (mantle), the paracord survival laces are the ones you’ll want to reach down for and tie up when preparing for your next outdoor adventure expedition or work day. Made in the USA, these survival hiking boot laces are highly abrasion, chemical, corrosion, mold, wear, tear and UV resistant, amounting to an incredibly strong, durable and reliable product, sure to outlast any other shoe or boot laces that you’re currently using.<br><br>Here are the specs you’ll want to note:<br>- Made in USA<br>- Sold as a pair (or set of two laces)<br>- 4</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- MAIN DESCRIPTION -->\n\n\n\t<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t/* FONTS AND COLORS */\n\t\tbody {\n\t\t\tfont-family: Arial,sans-serif;\n\t\t\tfont-size: 14px;\n\t\t\tline-height: 1.428571429;\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t\tbackground-color: white;\n\t\t}\n\t\th1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {\n\t\t\tcolor: black;\n\t\t}\n\t\tp {\n\t\t\twhite-space: pre-line;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.navbar a, .navbar a:active, .navbar a:hover, .navbar a:visited {\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.product-specs {\n\t\t\tbackground-color: #f1f1f1;\n\t\t\tpadding: 1em;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.product-specs td {\n\t\t\tfont-size:12px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-left {\n\t\t\tmin-width:6em;\n\t\t\tfont-weight:bold;\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-right {\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tdiv.footer {\n\t\t\tborder-top: 1px solid #f1f1f1;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.navbar-default {\n\t\t\tbackground-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);\n\t\t\tbackground-image: linear-gradien